title: FREE Android app - Guide of linux commands
description:
This application serves as a guide of various commands that can be used in a terminal GNU / Linux and even on your android phone.
It covers how to navigate directories, create and delete users and other useful commands.
Over time we will be adding new commands and features (search for commands, add custom commands, among a few others).
Many of these commands also work on your android phone, just have a Terminal application.
If you want to send a tip and or suggestions, please send to our email.
* This application uses Google Analytics technology
